SIGNMESSAGE.SIGN_DESCRIPTION: Waxaad kugeli kartaa fariimo cinwaanadaada si aad u xaqiijiso inaad iyaga leedahay. Ka taxadar inaadan saxeexin wax aan caddayn, sida weerarrada phishing waxay isku dayi karaan inay kugu saxaan inaad saxiixdo aqoonsigaaga iyaga. Kaliya saxiix dhammaan waraaqo faahfaahsan oo aad ku raacsan tahay.
SIGNMESSAGE.VERIFY_DESCRIPTION: Ku qor cinwaanka saxiixa, farriin (hubi inaad nuqul ka gooysay jadwalka, meelaha, saxsanaha, iwm.) Iyo saxiixa hoose si loo xaqiijiyo fariinta. Ka digtoonow inaadan wax badan ku qorin saxeexa inta uu ku jiro farriinta saxda ah ee lafteeda, si looga fogaado in uu khiyaaneeyo weerarka ninka dhex-dhexaad ah.

REPAIR.INFOEXTERNAL: Amaradaas dayactiradani ma shaqeyn karaan marka Metrix Core ay si kedis ah u socoto
REPAIR.INFO: Qeybaha hoose waxay dib u bilaabi doonaan Metrix Core kala doorashooyinka taliska si ay u dayactiraan jeebka, wax ka qabtaan arrimaha faylasha qashinka ah ama maqanaansho / maqnaansho dhaqaale.
REPAIR.SALVAGEINFO: -hadal-guri-guri: Isku day in aad ka soo qaadato furayaasha gaarka ah ee ka soo jeeda jeebka.
REPAIR.RECOVER1INFO: -zapwallettxes = 1: Dib u soo celinta macaamilada blockchain (haysashada macluumaadka meta, tus.
REPAIR.RECOVER2INFO: -zapwallettxes = 2: Dib u soo celinta macaamilada ee blockchain
REPAIR.UPGRADEWALLETINFO: -grgradewallet: Xaqiijinta kumbuyuutarka si aad uhesho qaabka ugu dambeeya ee bilowga. (Fiiro gaar ah: Tani ma aha cusbooneysiin ee boorsada lafteeda!)
REPAIR.REBUILDINDEXINFO: -reindex: Dib u cusbooneysii index of blockchain laga bilaabo faylasha datka ee hadda.
REPAIR.BOOTSTRAPINFO: Ka soo dejista faylasha Metrix blockchain ee ka socda metrixcoin.com oo kabaha xirxiro rakibaaddaada. Waxay kuxirantahay xirnaankaaga shabakada tani waxay qaadan kartaa 10 daqiiqo ilaa dhowr saacadood
REPAIR.SYNCFROMSTARTINFO: Ka tirtir faylalkaaga 'blockchain' iyo resync-ka kana soo dhego hiddo-wadaha.
REPAIR.RESTARTCOREINFO: Dib-u-bilaw Metrix Core haddii uu horeba u shaqeynayay ama bilaw Metrix Core haddii uusan shaqeynaynin.
REPAIR.REINSTALLCOREINFO: Ka tirtir Metrix Core-ga deegaankaaga oo dib uga xir server-yada Metrix.

PROMPT.ENCRYPTEDCONTENT: Dhamaan kormeerkii hore ee aad ka sameysey faylka boorsadaada waa in lagu bedelaa faylka cusub ee la abuuray, oo la buuxiyey. Sababaha nabadgelyada awgood, nuquladii hore ee feylka aan la isticmaalin ayaa faa'iido u noqon doonta sida ugu dhakhsaha badan ee aad u bilowdo isticmaalka kumbuyuutarka cusub, oo loo yaqaan 'encrypted'.

PROMPT.STARTUPFAILEDINFO: Waxaa jiray bilaw Metrix Core. Waxaa lagu talinayaa in aad fiiriso faylkaaga Altitude log ee arrimaha.
